<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
1. Initialized `minK` amd `maxK` index with -1 as there last Position means they haven't arrived.
2. `li` show last index of starting of valid subarray means in range of `minK` and `maxK`.
3. Then in Loop we allocating index according to alement arrival and also reseting if any out of `minK` and `maxK` arriving.
4. here `ans` is increasing when both the mni and mnx are arrived means they have not allocated -1 as there index.
4. returning `ans`.

